      <title>涉嫌中国干预促使外国代理人在加拿大注册</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/alleged-chinese-meddling-spurs-foreign-agent-registry-in-canada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理贾斯汀·特鲁多政府将要求游说或以其他方式代表外国政府行事的人公开登记该活动，此举是在中国试图干预加拿大最近两次选举的指控之后采取的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/alleged-chinese-meddling-spurs-foreign-agent-registry-in-canada</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 20:41:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉推动巴西抗洪救灾免受支出规定约束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/lula-pushes-to-exempt-brazil-flood-relief-from-spending-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦提议将紧急支出排除在巴西财政规则之外，因为他的政府正在加紧应对该国南部地区的毁灭性洪水。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/lula-pushes-to-exempt-brazil-flood-relief-from-spending-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 20:40:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称前往俄罗斯的士兵因“不当行为”而被拘留</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/us-says-soldier-detained-in-russia-accused-of-misconduct</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国陆军周一表示，一名美国士兵因“不当行为指控”在俄罗斯东部被拘留，这可能成为自俄罗斯 2022 年 2 月入侵乌克兰以来两国关系已经处于低谷的新爆发点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/us-says-soldier-detained-in-russia-accused-of-misconduct</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 19:51:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列称哈马斯支持的停火计划远远不够</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/hamas-says-accepts-proposal-for-cease-fire-with-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴勒斯坦激进组织哈马斯表示已同意加沙地带停火提议，但以色列战时内阁一致拒绝该提议，称其“与以色列的必要要求相去甚远”，使立即暂停战斗的希望破灭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/hamas-says-accepts-proposal-for-cease-fire-with-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 16:59:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前特朗普财务总监称科恩从个人账户中还款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/trump-found-in-contempt-a-second-time-in-hush-money-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名前特朗普组织财务官员告诉纽约一家法院，唐纳德·特朗普使用个人银行账户偿还了他欠一位前律师的大部分钱，该律师在 2016 年大选前收买了成人电影明星斯托米·丹尼尔斯的沉默。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/trump-found-in-contempt-a-second-time-in-hush-money-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 13:34:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经过数周的动荡后，哥伦比亚大学取消了主要毕业典礼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/columbia-cancels-university-wide-commencement-ceremony</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于以色列与哈马斯战争引发的抗议活动扰乱了大学毕业季，哥伦比亚大学在校园内经历了数周的骚乱后，取消了原定于 5 月 15 日举行的主要毕业典礼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/columbia-cancels-university-wide-commencement-ceremony</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 13:09:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>更多风暴袭击休斯顿地区，数百人从洪水中获救</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-05-05/hundreds-rescued-from-texas-floods-as-forecast-calls-for-more-rain-and-rising-water</link>
      <description><![CDATA[休斯顿（美联社）——周日，德克萨斯州的暴风雨给已经饱和的休斯敦地区带来了额外的降雨，数百人从被洪水淹没的房屋和道路中获救，而在北部的沃斯堡地区，一名儿童在乘坐汽车时被冲走后死亡。被困在洪水中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-05-05/hundreds-rescued-from-texas-floods-as-forecast-calls-for-more-rain-and-rising-water</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 04:20:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
